sentences: Larkin Grimm (born September 18, 1981) is an American singer-songwriter and musician based in New York City.
Larkin's third album Parplar was released October 2008 by Young God Records.
In 2017 Grimm released her album Chasing an Illusion on Northern Spy Records.
